                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d17">
                <head>17. Telegram From the <gloss type="from">
                        <gloss target="#t_CIA1">CIA</gloss> Station</gloss> in [<hi rend="italic"
                        >place not declassified</hi>] to the <gloss type="to">Central Intelligence
                        Agency</gloss>
                    <note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d17fn1">Source: Central Intelligence Agency,
                        Job 79–01025A, Box 14, Folder 1. Top Secret; Routine.</note>
                </head>
                <dateline>[<hi rend="italic">place not declassified</hi>], <date
                        calendar="gregorian" when="1952-09-12T16:32:00+00:00">September 12, 1952,
                        1632Z</date>.</dateline>
                <p>[<hi rend="italic">telegram indicator not declassified</hi>] 605. Ref: <gloss
                        target="#t_DIR1">DIR</gloss> 18338.<note n="2" xml:id="d17fn2">Not
                        found.</note>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <persName corresp="#p_SGA1">Somoza</persName> advised Ambassador
                        <persName>Whelan</persName> that he and <persName corresp="#p_TMRL1"
                        >Trujillo</persName> have agreed on Guatemala and would take care of
                    situation. Venezuela apparently has agreed to cooperate. Details of <persName
                        corresp="#p_SGA1">Somoza</persName>–<persName corresp="#p_TMRL1"
                        >Trujillo</persName> agreement and plans not presently available. Source TNN
                    560 not yet <pb facs="0057" n="27" xml:id="pg_27"/> advised of plans but will
                    furnish on receipt. Due to illness and preoccupation with other matters
                        <persName corresp="#p_SGA1">Somoza</persName> has not yet briefed DYMAROON
                    on plans but has advised that he will do so. Advise if hqs desirous of receiving
                    information obtained from DYMAROON by cable.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
